    <div class="example" id="if-else">
      <h2><a href="./">Go в примери</a>: Ако ли/Иначе (If/Else)</h2>
      
      <table>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>Разклоняване<sup class="footnote-ref" id="fnref:branching"><a href="#fn:branching">1</a></sup> на програмата с <code>if</code> и <code>else</code>
в Go е лесно.</p>

<div class="footnotes">

<hr />

<ol>
<li id="fn:branching">branching – разклоняване</li>
</ol>

</div>

          </td>
          <td class="code empty leading">
            
          
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            
          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            <a href="https://go.dev/play/p/FpZviBlPe5L"><img title="Run code" src="play.png" class="run" /></a><img title="Copy code" src="clipboard.png" class="copy" />
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kn">package</span> <span class="nx">main</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            
          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="s">&#34;fmt&#34;</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            
          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="kd">func</span> <span class="nf">main</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="p">{</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>Ето един прост пример.</p>

          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="mi">7</span><span class="o">%</span><span class="mi">2</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">0</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nx">fmt</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">Println</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;7 е четно&#34;</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">}</span> <span class="k">else</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nx">fmt</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">Println</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;7 е нечетно&#34;</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>Може да имате изявление <code>if</code> без <code>else</code>.</p>

          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="mi">8</span><span class="o">%</span><span class="mi">4</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">0</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nx">fmt</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">Println</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;8 се дели на 4&#34;</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>Логически действия като <code>&amp;&amp;</code> и <code>||</code> често се срещат
в условия.</p>

          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="mi">8</span><span class="o">%</span><span class="mi">2</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">0</span> <span class="o">||</span> <span class="mi">7</span><span class="o">%</span><span class="mi">2</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="mi">0</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nx">fmt</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">Println</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">&#34;или 8, или 7 е четно&#34;</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>Условията могат да бъдад предшествани от изявление.
Всички променливи, обявени в изявлението, могат да се
ползват в текущото и всички последващи разклонения.</p>

          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="nx">num</span> <span class="o">:=</span> <span class="mi">9</span><span class="p">;</span> <span class="nx">num</span> <span class="p">&lt;</span> <span class="mi">0</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nx">fmt</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">Println</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">num</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">&#34;е отрицателно&#34;</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">}</span> <span class="k">else</span> <span class="k">if</span> <span class="nx">num</span> <span class="p">&lt;</span> <span class="mi">10</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nx">fmt</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">Println</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">num</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">&#34;е едноцифрено число&#34;</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">}</span> <span class="k">else</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">        <span class="nx">fmt</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nf">Println</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">num</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="s">&#34;е многоцифрено&#34;</span><span class="p">)</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    <span class="p">}</span>
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="p">}</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>Обърнете внимание, че не се нуждаете от кръгли скоби
около условията, както е в повечето други езици за
програмиране.</p>

          </td>
          <td class="code empty">
            
          
          </td>
        </tr>
        
      </table>
      
      <table>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            
          </td>
          <td class="code leading">
            
          <pre class="chroma"><code><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="gp">$</span> go run if-else.go
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">7 is odd
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">8 is divisible by 4
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">either 8 or 7 are even
</span></span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"><span class="go">9 has 1 digit</span></span></span></code></pre>
          </td>
        </tr>
        
        <tr>
          <td class="docs">
            <p>В Го няма троично &ldquo;ако&rdquo; (<a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%3F:">ternary if</a>).
Така че трябва винаги да се ползва пълното изявление
<code>if</code> дори за съвсем прости условия.</p>

          </td>
          <td class="code empty">
            
          
          </td>
        </tr>
        
